{"tid":749226,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[捉蟲] 有冇巴絲打有興趣聽日一齊去川龍捉昆蟲？","createTime":"2018-07-20T00:58:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T00:58:23.000Z","uid":171929,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8b5b0c4f6f19764317e3b8191a1782b6236961bf","tid":749226,"uid":171929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T00:58:23.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n小弟我返intern個非牟利機構開始咗一個好有意思嘅project，就係希望可以用民間嘅力量一齊研究香港昆蟲嘅生物多樣性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/20/081708_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F20%2F081708_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=656718d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然香港係一個石屎森林，但其實昆蟲嘅種類同數目都十分之多，有時候甚至會發現到香港獨有嘅物種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/20/082150_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F20%2F082150_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=373261b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nE.g. 2011年發現嘅米埔屈翅螢係香港獨有種，現時只知道會係濕地公園同天水圍一帶出沒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(Photo &amp; info Credit: 香港螢火蟲by 饒戈)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/20/083923_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F20%2F083923_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=7a11c160&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地希望可以建立一個由民間力量而製成嘅香港昆蟲資料庫，除咗會有昆蟲標本之外，我地仲會將搵到嘅部分昆蟲做DNA Barcoding，從而建立一個香港昆蟲嘅DNA barcoding library，繼而將依啲數據提交比一啲國際性嘅DNA barcoding database，為世界物種多樣性研究作出貢獻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地聽日就會出發去第一次正式Field trip，到川龍捉蟲！ 各位巴絲打如果有興趣，可以去下邊條Link報名；如果唔得閒，都可以like我地個facebook，依個夏天我地都keep 住會有唔同類型同bio有關嘅活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nLink for registration: <a href=\"https://www.eventbrite.hk/e/bug-hunt-field-trip-tickets-47803122426\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eventbrite.hk%2Fe%2Fbug-hunt-field-trip-tickets-47803122426&d=KR2iNJyhpgUPMk8BaXJNfZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=7a7209dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eventbrite.hk/e/bug-hunt-field-trip-tickets-47803122426</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/DIYBIOHongKong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FDIYBIOHongKong%2F&d=KR2iNJyhpgUPMk8BaXJNfZUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=3606c5bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/DIYBIOHongKong/</a><br />\n<br />\n希望聽日會見到你地啦！<br />\n<br />\n------<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 大家可能會疑問點解一個「捉蟲」嘅活動都會收錢，咁係因為我地會提供一個捉昆蟲嘅專用套裝，同埋都想收返少少錢幫補實驗室嘅日常運作。<br />\n<br />\n依個機構本身係非牟利，上至Director，下至我依啲intern仔，都係燃燒對bio嘅熱愛係到義務工作，全部人都係冇人工，甚至travel allowance都冇。所以希望大家了解點解我地決定會為今次嘅field trip收費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}